channel.description:
[center][size=24pt]Project Incomprehensible Quality[/size]
[b]We are origional from rune-server[/b]
[b]Layout:[/b] [b]iQuality is going to be a stable, medium economical server with many many features. There will be as much as Skilling as Pking to improve the economy. Every skill will be available to train even the construction, hunter and summoning skill. We would like to introduce 4 main PK-ing spots: Bounty hunter, edgeville, mage bank and varrock level 1 for some multi-combat pking. The whole world map will be used for skilling (e.g not a ''skill teleport''). The minigames and monsters are there to obtain items: Barrows, Barbarian assault. We also have entertainment minigames : Fight pits, duel arena, duel tournaments, Castle Wars. Therefore there will be rewards for playing these minigames, atleast some of them.[/b]

Rewrite slayer system Working stairs system Clue's (level 1,2,3) Fix citys (add npcs+shops) Constitution Bank pins Every lunar spell Following Rip korasi formula somewhere Rewrite fight pits + caves Double exp weekend every weekend
